title: First-Line Supervisors of Weapons Specialists/Crew Members
descr: Supervise and coordinate the activities of weapons specialists/crew members. Supervisors may also perform the same activities as the workers they supervise.
alt_titles: Armament Weapons Support Equipment (ASWE) Maintenance Manager, Armor Senior Sergeant, Field Artillery Senior Sergeant, Infantry Unit Leader, Over The Horizon-Targeting (OTH-T) Supervisor, Aerial Gunner, Superintendent, Air Defense Artillery Senior Sergeant, Airborne Weapons Technical Manager
